# Cursor Rules for MudBlazor Project

## MudBlazor Component Recognition
- Enable IntelliSense for MudBlazor components
- Recognize MudBlazor component prefixes (Mud*)
- Provide autocomplete for MudBlazor properties and events

## Razor File Configuration
- Treat .razor files as Blazor components
- Enable syntax highlighting for MudBlazor components
- Provide IntelliSense for MudBlazor component attributes

## Project Structure
- Recognize Blazor Server project structure
- Enable proper namespace resolution for MudBlazor
- Support for component discovery and navigation

## IntelliSense Settings
- Enable Roslyn analyzers
- Enable import completion
- Enable async completion
- Enable tag helper completion for MudBlazor components
